    <item>
      <title>[线性代数] 8.伴随矩阵&amp;逆矩阵的性质</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/8.%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jul 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/8.%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[线性代数] 8.伴随矩阵&逆矩阵的性质</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="性质">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%80%a7%e8%b4%a8"></a>
性质
</h2><p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/8.%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%A8/image-20260704222434801.png" alt="image-20260704222434801"></p>
<p>来自定义式:
</p>
$$
AA^* = A^*A = |A|E
$$<p>
来自定义式:
</p>
$$
AA^{-1} = A^{-1}A = E
$$<p>
则:
</p>
$$
A^{-1} = \frac{1}{|A|}A^*
\\
(A^*)^{-1} = \frac{1}{|A|}A
$$
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-04首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-04</p>]]>
