    <item>
      <title>[线性代数] 7.逆矩阵</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/7.%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jul 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/7.%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[线性代数] 7.逆矩阵</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="逆矩阵">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e9%80%86%e7%9f%a9%e9%98%b5"></a>
逆矩阵
</h2><h4 id="1-定义式求逆矩阵">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e5%ae%9a%e4%b9%89%e5%bc%8f%e6%b1%82%e9%80%86%e7%9f%a9%e9%98%b5"></a>
1. 定义式求逆矩阵
</h4><p>定义式:
</p>
$$
AA^{-1}=A^{-1}A=E
$$<blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/7.%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/image-20260704221339232.png" alt="image-20260704221339232"></p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="2-伴随矩阵求逆矩阵">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#2-%e4%bc%b4%e9%9a%8f%e7%9f%a9%e9%98%b5%e6%b1%82%e9%80%86%e7%9f%a9%e9%98%b5"></a>
2. 伴随矩阵求逆矩阵
</h4><p>核心公式: (前提是行列式不为0)
</p>
$$
AA^*=|A|E \quad \Rightarrow \quad \mathbf{A^{-1}=\frac{1}{|A|}A^*}
$$<blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/7.%E9%80%86%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/image-20260704222017305.png" alt="image-20260704222017305"></p>
</blockquote>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-04首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-04</p>]]>
