    <item>
      <title>[线性代数] 6.伴随矩阵</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/6.%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jul 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/6.%E4%BC%B4%E9%9A%8F%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[线性代数] 6.伴随矩阵</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="伴随矩阵">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%bc%b4%e9%9a%8f%e7%9f%a9%e9%98%b5"></a>
伴随矩阵
</h2><p>若矩阵$A$:
</p>
$$
A =
\begin{bmatrix}
a_{11} & a_{12} & \dots & a_{1n} \\
a_{21} & a_{22} & \dots & a_{2n} \\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots \\
a_{n1} & a_{n2} & \dots & a_{nn}
\end{bmatrix}
$$<p>
则伴随矩阵$A^*$:
</p>
$$
A^* =
\begin{bmatrix}
A_{11} & A_{21} & \dots & A_{n1} \\
A_{12} & A_{22} & \dots & A_{n2} \\
\vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots \\
A_{1n} & A_{2n} & \dots & A_{nn}
\end{bmatrix}
$$<blockquote>
<p>其中元素为代数余子式, 且整体转置过</p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-04首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-04</p>]]>
      </description>
      
        <category>线性代数</category>
      
    </item>
    
    

    <item>
      <title>[线性代数] 5.矩阵</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/5.%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jul 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/5.%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[线性代数] 5.矩阵</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="矩阵">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%9f%a9%e9%98%b5"></a>
矩阵
</h2><p>不同于行列式:</p>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/5.%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/image-20260704131604903.png" alt="image-20260704131604903"></p>
<p>运算:
</p>
$$
(A+B)^2=A^2+AB+BA+B^2
$$<p>
规则:
</p>
$$
AB = AC \nLeftrightarrow B = C
$$<h2 id="方阵的幂">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%96%b9%e9%98%b5%e7%9a%84%e5%b9%82"></a>
方阵的幂
</h2><blockquote>
<p><img src="/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%A3%E6%95%B0/5.%E7%9F%A9%E9%98%B5/image-20260704133350301.png" alt="image-20260704133350301"></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="转置">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e8%bd%ac%e7%bd%ae"></a>
转置
</h2><h4 id="1-一般">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e4%b8%80%e8%88%ac"></a>
1. 一般
</h4><ul>
<li>$(A^T)^T = A$</li>
<li>$(A+B)^T = A^T + B^T$</li>
<li>$(AB)^T = B^T A^T$</li>
<li>$(A^n)^T=(A^T)^n$</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="2-特殊">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#2-%e7%89%b9%e6%ae%8a"></a>
2. 特殊
</h4><p>对称矩阵: $A^T=A$</p>
<ul>
<li>主对角线两侧的元素对称相等</li>
</ul>
<p>反对称矩阵: $A^T=-A$</p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-04首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-04</p>]]>
      </description>
      
        <category>线性代数</category>
      
    </item>
    
    

